Hello,

This css_unic_swat, the action takes place in a part of the Swat 's valley in Pakistan.

The map is designed to be a deathmatch team challenge, the size is medium.

The map runs very well with about  24 players, more its depend froom your configuration.

Many ways are available between rocks and building, you should be able to climb in certains rocks and buildings, walls...

Many places  available to ambush, sniping.

Auto meshes (ladders custom incorporated) provided.

Enjoy It
